ecause implementation cost was recently incurred\",\"Promote on one performance benchmark\",\"Keep undocumented shadow and persistent modes as a compromise\"],\"focusTrack\":\"decision\",\"edgeCase\":\"ambiguous-input\",\"toolsUsed\":[\"Read\",\"Grep\"],\"sourcesQueried\":[\"consumer feature-token search\",\"002-js-capabilities/spec.md\",\"003-measured-native/spec.md\",\"004-growth/spec.md\",\"gap-analysis.md\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-21T08:48:20Z\",\"durationMs\":196000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-sol-high-fast-1784622756165-kgdopz\",\"generation\":1,\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\"},\"graphEvents\":[]}\n{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"dashboard_generated\",\"iteration\":4,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-21T08:48:21Z\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-sol-high-fast-1784622756165-kgdopz\",\"generation\":1}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":5,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"run\":5,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Adversarial validation and complete wire/shelf execution plans\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":0.43,\"noveltyJustification\":\"The bounded blast radius and both sequenced execution plans are new; the final recommendation consolidates prior evidence.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"What are the safe wiring and deprecation plans?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"What are the safe wiring and deprecation plans?\"],\"ruledOut\":[\"Delete the flat retrieval manifest when shelving\",\"Leave database environment and CLI switches live after shelving\",\"Build the database lazily on query\",\"Wire without clean-checkout distribution ownership\",\"Keep dormant runtime as a compromise\"],\"focusTrack\":\"execution\",\"edgeCase\":\"contradictory-evidence\",\"toolsUsed\":[\"Read\",\"Grep\"],\"sourcesQueried\":[\"DB mode/import dependency search\",\"retrieval manifest ownership search\",\"engine test index\",\"c